OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDean Mears had "no significant mental
OL,8,Fdisorder" when he killed a
OL,9,Fgrandmother, according to an expert at
OL,10,FCaernarfon Crown court.
OL,12,FCatherine Flynn, 69, of Cefndy Road in
OL,13,FRhyl, died on 25 October.
OL,15,FToday jurors heard conflicting
OL,16,Faccounts as another psychiatrist for
OL,17,Fthe defence argued the defendant, Dean
OL,18,FMark Albert Mears, 34, of Bodelwyddan
OL,19,FAvenue in Kinmel, displayed symptoms
OL,20,Fof PTSD at the time of the killing.
