OL,4,C'significant mental disorder', court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDr Shepherd said he believes the
OL,8,Fdefendant was suffering from
OL,9,Fdepressive and adjustment disorder,
OL,10,Fand post-traumatic stress disorder
OL,11,Ffollowing a stabbing, all complicated
OL,12,Fby his drug use.
OL,14,FFor the prosecution, psychiatrist Dr
OL,15,FJohn Sandford told the jury in his
OL,16,Fprofessional view Mears does not
OL,17,Fcurrently suffer from a severe mental
OL,18,Fillness, and has not in the past.
